enum ErrorCode
 

ErrorCode Error codes that can occur during tests.

Enumerator:
ST_ERR_ALLOCATION  Error during memory allocation.
ST_ERR_SOCKALLOC  Error during socket allocation.
ST_ERR_CLOSE  Error while closing socket.
ST_ERR_WRONGDATA  Wrong data received on socket.
ST_ERR_USERINTERRUPT  User or timeout stopped test.
ST_ERR_WRITESOCK_CONTEXT  Lost context or data connection.
ST_ERR_WRITESOCK_UNKNOWN  Error during writing data if GetError() returns 0.
ST_ERR_NOT_ALL_PACKETS_RECEIVED  Socket did not receive all packets.
ST_ERR_SET_DATACONN_PROFILE_ID  Setting the data connection profile ID to the socket failed.
ST_ERR_SERVER_SOCK_LISTEN  Putting a server socket into listen state failed.
